{"tid":689560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲法庭紀錄，「唐琳玲」5年前曾襲警被罰999澳元","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:45:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bba6c5934b228a1d38afe9785e3a715cbadef5e2","tid":689560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1499380/org/15c9b56894bbdbfc5cc9257211f8977e.jpg/vz3pHwwh-XyMiZtLcOZNhA5YJH3WQ6kNiIQckYiEHJE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1499380%2Forg%2F15c9b56894bbdbfc5cc9257211f8977e.jpg%2Fvz3pHwwh-XyMiZtLcOZNhA5YJH3WQ6kNiIQckYiEHJE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=194fa28d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n支那婆唐琳玲（35歲）疑在庭上拍照的案情，似乎每日都有富娛樂性的發展。唐先是氣焰指出可和法官自拍、被揭履歷和名片造假、後因無繳付保釋金被拘捕、又被揭報住假地址，之後又在庭上稱耶穌指她無辜。<br />\n<br />\n雖然唐今日在法院被判刑，但事件餘波未了。《香港01》記者發現，一名與唐琳玲英文全名拼法相同、同年齡的女子，在澳洲悉尼有多項襲警案底，被判近1,000澳元罰款及堂費。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》記者未能確立該名澳洲被告，是否就是唐琳玲本人。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/194262/庭上拍照-澳洲法庭紀錄-唐琳玲-5年前曾襲警被罰999澳元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F194262%2F%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E5%94%90%E7%90%B3%E7%8E%B2-5%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E6%9B%BE%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%B0999%E6%BE%B3%E5%85%83&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcAb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c341e2d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/194262/庭上拍照-澳洲法庭紀錄-唐琳玲-5年前曾襲警被罰999澳元</a>"},{"pid":"ea3c92fb1fd82a56a95f6a76c0b5956a77c2abe0","tid":689560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"香港01查找澳洲新南威爾士州地區法院案件資料，並與法院職員再三核實，發現一名為「TANG Lin Ling 」、生於1983年11月的女性，曾於2013年被判三項襲警刑事罪行。該名澳洲被告的姓名的英文譯音與唐琳玲相同，二人今年均為35歲。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1497306/org/3a95b9fb9f89cfda0cddbb507835e8dc.jpg/svfM-rOdShm1Ksxm3LeNW58-zCZaTyEJ0Qa3y9EGt8s?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1497306%2Forg%2F3a95b9fb9f89cfda0cddbb507835e8dc.jpg%2FsvfM-rOdShm1Ksxm3LeNW58-zCZaTyEJ0Qa3y9EGt8s%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=69a8f973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唐琳玲言論突出，多日以來受傳媒追訪。</span></div>"},{"pid":"14b654d2b602d676c6c23e916414ba6289b8bade","tid":689560,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:29:07.000Z","msg":"唐琳玲在庭上經常提到自己的澳洲背景，包括早前向香港法官指自己曾居於澳洲、認為自己的英語帶有澳洲口音、因喜歡香港而放棄移居澳洲等。其網上履歷亦聲稱自己曾於2010至2012年間，在悉尼大學供讀碩士。而大律師艾勤賢早前亦於庭上表示，唐向他自我介紹時，向他遞上卡片後，便表示於悉尼大學畢業。<br />\n<br />\n不過，就現有資料，《香港01》記者未能確立該名澳洲被告，是否就是唐琳玲本人。記者暫時未能取得唐的回應。"},{"pid":"a2224c67d6ccab068dda2402bfe55e990c003412","tid":689560,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做你癡線當棄子，跟手返去又換過身份落黎開工！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c07ba101797e3bd6eb1ba59d31c165a4f4e8e53a","tid":689560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842ed0b8f33d5312b02c285593455c5df07ad665","tid":689560,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"點落到黎香港 入境處解釋下好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd6ddcc36002fc73e277928cb4feceeb82205c9","tid":689560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"據澳洲案件記錄，一名為「TANG Lin Ling 」女性於2012年11月15日被落案起訴刑事罪行，並於2013年2月13日，在位於悉尼的地區法院上庭，控罪包括兩項襲擊正執行任務警員罪（Assault officer in execution of duty）以及一項拒絕及防礙警察執行任務罪名（Resist or hinder police officer in the execution of duty）。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1497322/org/037c1388f027baf003ed0a7aac06cb81.png/U91jCWvrwwFDyB8OmBwpbwV1nY45_Glywg8lC8IPJQs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1497322%2Forg%2F037c1388f027baf003ed0a7aac06cb81.png%2FU91jCWvrwwFDyB8OmBwpbwV1nY45_Glywg8lC8IPJQs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=cfd6a0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">跟據悉尼法院資料，一名為「Lin Ling TANG」的35歲女子，在澳洲有三宗定罪記錄。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n被告三項刑事罪名均被定罪，每項被判250澳元罰款及83元訟費，三項共約750澳元罰款及249澳元堂費，即合共近6,000港元。被告曾就每項判刑申請上訴，但不獲接納。<br />\n<br />\n另外，悉尼大學發言人回覆《香港01》記者查詢，指2012年確有一名為「Lin Ling Tang」女子取得商業碩士學位（Master of Commerce），而唐琳玲則在其LinkedIn網頁聲稱自己該年畢業於悉尼大學的會計及金融碩士（Master of Accounting and Finance）。《香港01》未能確認該名碩士生是否唐琳玲本人。"},{"pid":"cfff465b67d09904f157ae8138bed3333d98b3ab","tid":689560,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:51:18.000Z","msg":"個底花晒...<br />\n<br />\n聽我一個住過澳洲朋友講，有CR出去去英文國家、西方國家甚至日韓去旅行、移民都會有困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n疊埋心水返支那做海龜呃人喇柒頭"},{"pid":"19e1bdb8ffa4b9be0ea3a339ff85fad9d56fed5f","tid":689560,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個底花晒...<br />\n<br />\n聽我一個住過澳洲朋友講，有CR去英文國家、西方國家甚至日韓去旅行、移民都會有困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n疊埋心水返支那做海龜呃人喇柒頭</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bb7e8d78aae3bcd10423e967eb35deebc0308589","tid":689560,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:52:20.000Z","msg":"有錢去澳洲, 背後無金主都無人信"},{"pid":"06e38ac07bf6ccb788721833057ce2f12f6f6b6b","tid":689560,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"842ed0b8f33d5312b02c285593455c5df07ad665","tid":689560,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"點落到黎香港 入境處解釋下好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"而家d入境部門算吧喇<br />\n連屍骨龍都可以申請到落黎<br />\n<br />\n真係殺人放火屍骨龍，條橋鋪路無港人"},{"pid":"3d69afaeaf05d4a9cbff98a41f0713e49b99bbd1","tid":689560,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"真係国鏟零零柒，short咗嗰隻，蝈安都好頭痕。"},{"pid":"52afe7cafcf9ba3c75f68e68b143af23ece065b9","tid":689560,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"中共冇人才咩? 唔搵個大波長腿???"},{"pid":"e2058de6c907b744f2fc6867e726cd443efbc308","tid":689560,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"話之你喺外國殺過人<br />\n只要係黃皮膚黑眼睛講普通話<br />\n就可以黎香港做專才攞身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5ba4ba1a6b1414b85f222118032e69fa5409c0","tid":689560,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"仆你個街<br />\n班所謂專才有幾多係好似呢條傻西咁"},{"pid":"d89caf1adb0fda2357afb0766c6750d5a680b22c","tid":689560,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾傳媒<br />\n《香港01》記者未能確立該名澳洲被告，是否就是唐琳玲本人。<br />\n<br />\n同標題兩回事"}]}